    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3; this gap is accepted given ASTM F1717 is the recognized regulatory standard for this device class and no alternative multi-condition test protocol exists. All three QoIs pass quantitative acceptance criteria across both laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device.",
